{
  "text": "If we are only interested in the sums (or the range-sums), the DLT priority sampling algorithm would be ideal, especially for positive data [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . Although the priority sampling algorithm had been proposed and implemented commercially for a few years, only recently [CITATION_4] proved the non-asymptotic variance (bound) and the best constant.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "651089",
